return {title = "R Key", id = 636, description = {'In Greed Mode and while playing as Tainted Keeper, this item costs 99 coins instead of 15', 'Allows angel rooms to be found in the new run if a devil deal was taken in the first run', 'Donation machines become fixed if they were jammed before using the R Key', "When used in the backwards path after picking up Dad's Note, R key will skip you to the Basement 1 version of this path, which leads directly to the Home floor. This may cause you to skip floors where you left a trinket to spawn a Cracked Key.", 'The game timer does not reset', 'When used, this item restarts the game and places you back on the first floor with all your currently collected items, similar to doing a Victory Lap'}}